we only need one of these notebooks.

276
00:20:55,680 --> 00:20:56,560
I'll return it to you.

277
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:10,040
People who use the notebook are cursed with misfortune, huh?

278
00:21:10,370 --> 00:21:13,520
